  start_row=0
  increment=30
  for(x in 1:5){
  print(paste("start_row:",start_row))
  df_small<-df[start_row:(start_row+increment),]
  print(dim(df_small))
  #print(df_small)
  start_row=start_row+increment
  }
}

  ggplot(data = df, aes(x=Date, y=Sales)) +
  geom_point() +
  labs(x = "Date",
    y = "Daily Sales",
    title = "Sales vs. Day",
